history.proof: intros n m. induction n. - simpl. apply Nat.le_0_l. - simpl. rewrite Nat.mul_succ_r. apply le_S. qsimpl time: 1.

exceptions.exn: In environment n, m : nat IHn : n * m <= n * S m Unable to unify "n * m <= n * S m" with "m + n * m <= m + (n * m + n)".

original: intros n m. induction n. - simpl. apply Nat.le_0_l. - simpl. rewrite Nat.mul_succ_r. apply le_S. apply IHn.
